name: PhiLashes Hydrogel Pads
short_description: Hydrogel Eye Pads are specially designed for sensitive skin and eyes and are highly recommended for customers who have sensitive skin or eye spots. Contains 10 pairs. Lint Free
long_description: Hydrogel Eye Pads are specially designed for sensitive skin and eyes and are highly recommended for customers who have sensitive skin or eye spots. They are very thin and light, are used for professional eyelash extensions to keep the lower lashes in place for easy application. Contains hydrogel and other ingredients to avoid irritation.  Contains 10 pairs. Lint Free
